description:
@etsuyo623 made us fall in love with Japan in Spring even more!🌸

💡Spring in Japan is a time of new beginnings, as everything around comes back to life. It's a time when the cherry blossoms bloom and everything is suffused with a delicate and ethereal beauty. The air is filled with the aroma of sakura flowers, and the landscapes are painted with the colors of spring. It's a time of festivals, celebrations, and traditional customs that showcase the beauty and diversity of Japanese culture. If you want to experience the splendor of springtime in Japan, it's truly a sight to behold.

👉Share this with someone you want to visit Japan with!💕
